sources.name: AzureSqlTable1
sources.script:
source(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> AzureSqlTable1

typeProperties.script:
section Section1;
shared AzureSqlTable1 = let
  AdfDoc = Sql.Database("bireports.database.windows.net", "RisaBiReports", [CreateNavigationProperties = false]),
  InputTable = AdfDoc{[Schema = "dbo", Item = "Ditio"]}[Data]
in
  InputTable;
shared UserQuery = let
  Source = AzureSqlTable1
in
  Source;
shared Aktivitet_prosjekt_tid = let
  Source = UserQuery,
  #"Removed other columns" = Table.SelectColumns(Source, {"ProjectNumber", "ResourceNumber", "StartDateTime"}),
  #"Replaced value" = Table.ReplaceValue(#"Removed other columns", "T", " ", Replacer.ReplaceText, {"StartDateTime"}),
  #"Replaced value 1" = Table.ReplaceValue(#"Replaced value", "Z", "", Replacer.ReplaceText, {"StartDateTime"}),
  #"Sorted rows" = Table.Sort(#"Replaced value 1", {{"ResourceNumber", Order.Ascending}, {"StartDateTime", Order.Ascending}}),
  #"Changed column type" = Table.TransformColumns(#"Sorted rows", {{"StartDateTime", each DateTime.FromText(_, [Format = "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss", Culture = "nb-NO"]), type datetime}}),
  #"Filtered rows" = Table.SelectRows(#"Changed column type", each [ResourceNumber] <> null and [ResourceNumber] <> "")
in
  #"Filtered rows";
